-decoration: underline }</style></p>\r\n\r\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">p { margin-bottom: 0.25cm; direction: ltr; line-height: 115%; text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background: transparent }a:link { color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline }</style></p><p><br></p>', 'Hello {firstname} {lastname}\n\n\nYour job has been completed successfully.\n\nYour outstanding bill is also attached in this mail. Kindly proceed to make payment via our secure online platform or offline by paying to any of our designated banks within six hours as contained in the diagnostic bill.\n\nYour special 7 days warranty on job completion is now active with FixMaster!\n\nPlease click here to make payment on outstanding invoice\n\nWe look forward to your job rating and review on our website. Thank you for allowing us serve you!', 'CUSTOMER_JOB_COMPLETED_NOTIFICATION', '2021-06-15 12:28:24', '2021-06-15 12:28:24', NULL),
(33, '15cebc75-ac39-404c-ba39-cad0f29e5bf4', 'New Job Notification', '<p>\n\n\n	\n	\n	\n	\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 108%\">\nDear {firstname} {lastname}<br></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 108%\">A new job request\nis available for execution near you. Kindly login to your account to\nACCEPT the job NOW!</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 108%\"><font color=\"#222222\"><font face=\"Arial, serif\"><font style=\"font-size: 10pt\" size=\"2\">Please\nclick </font></font></font><font color=\"#222222\"><font face=\"Arial, serif\"><font style=\"font-size: 10pt\" size=\"2\">{url} to\nview details and accept the job request. </font></font></font>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.28cm; line-height: 108%\"><font color=\"#222222\"><font face=\"Arial, serif\"><font style=\"font-size: 10pt\" size=\"2\">Your\njob rating counts! Remember to request for a rating and review on all\ncompleted diagnosis and job repairs completed. &nbsp;</font></font></font></p>\n\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">p { margin-bottom: 0.25cm; direction: ltr; line-height: 115%; text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background: transparent }a:link { color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline }</style></p>', 'Dear {firstname} {lastname}\n\nA new job request is available for execution near you. Kindly login to your account to ACCEPT the job NOW!\n\nPlease click {url} to view details and accept the job request.\n\nYour job rating counts! Remember to request for a rating and review on all completed diagnosis and job repairs completed.', 'CSE_NEW_JOB_NOTIFICATION', '2021-06-16 06:34:11', '2021-06-16 06:34:11', NULL),
